snippet.title: Street Fighter X Mega Man reveal trailer
snippet.description:
Two worlds collide! Mega Man and the Street Fighters meet in this FREE PC download, coming to capcom-unity.com on December 17, 2012 - Mega Man's official 25th birthday.

Head to http://capcom-unity.com/mega_man for all the details!
